description:
For our next meetup, we’ve joined forces with a number of other Ruby user groups across Europe. We’ll meet (virtually) on June 9th at 4 pm for an action-packed mini-conference - view the schedule here. https://www.emeaonrails.com/#schedule

RSVP as soon as you can, and you’ll get the link to access the event nearer the time.

Look forward to seeing you soon!
title: South West Ruby #34 (ONLINE)
